a customer's feelings about their experience with a business.

89
00:05:35,000 --> 00:05:38,000
If you put something at the heart of things,

90
00:05:38,000 --> 00:05:40,000
you make it the most important part.

91
00:05:40,000 --> 00:05:44,000
Web traffic is the number of people visiting a website.

92
00:05:44,000 --> 00:05:49,000
Your legacy means all your life achievements that will continue after your death.

93
00:05:49,000 --> 00:05:55,000
Someone who's on the right side of history will be judged positively by future generations.

94
00:05:55,000 --> 00:05:59,000
And finally, greenwashing is when you pretend that your company is doing more

95
00:05:59,000 --> 00:06:02,000
to protect the environment than it really is.

